name: Pearl
author: The Mamas & The Papas
lyrics:
First star I see tonight, I wish I may, I wish I might
Have the wish I wish tonight.
A banker's daughter or a runaway girl, 
A little lady or a honky-tonk Pearl
Has to find someplace in this world where she feels at home.
I wish I may, I wish I might...
Have the wish I wish tonight.
